## Key Features Delivered

1. **Group Management**
   ✅ Create/update/delete groups
   ✅ Public and private groups
   ✅ Group discovery and search
   ✅ Location-based filtering

2. **Membership**
   ✅ Join/leave groups
   ✅ Approval workflow for private groups
   ✅ Member roles (Owner, Admin, Member)
   ✅ Invite system with shareable links

3. **Group Activities**
   ✅ Schedule group workouts
   ✅ Link to fitness classes
   ✅ RSVP system (Going/Maybe/Not Going)
   ✅ Recurring activities support

4. **Permissions & Security**
   ✅ Owner-only operations (delete group)
   ✅ Admin operations (approve requests, kick members)
   ✅ Member verification for activities
   ✅ JWT authentication on all protected endpoints

